    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty. It's basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single scratch or dent to be found! I've absolutely pampered this car, and it drives like a total dream. If you're looking for that 'new car' feel without the 'new car' price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Come take it for a spin, you're going to fall in love!",
