    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade E46 M3, a definitive pinnacle of the naturally aspirated S54 inline-six era. This specimen features a flawlessly calibrated double VANOS system and has undergone preventative rod bearing replacement to ensure peak internal tolerances. Power is delivered through a precise six-speed Getrag manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis is structurally sound with professional subframe reinforcement, maintaining optimal torsional rigidity. Finished in concours-level condition with an immaculate interior, this vehicle retains its original suspension geometry and factory-spec throttle response, offering the visceral, analog feedback sought by serious collectors.",
      "price": 48500.0,
