    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been meticulously garaged and kept in a climate-controlled environment throughout its life. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster with absolutely zero imperfections, swirls, or stone chips. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and entirely free of wear, while every electronic component, button, and safety feature functions exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, accompanied by a comprehensive service history documenting every scheduled maintenance interval performed by certified technicians. From the pristine engine bay to the untouched trunk lining, every detail reflects a life of pampered ownership. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade investment for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained in absolute showroom condition. This unit serves as a definitive benchmark for the model, boasting an unblemished aesthetic and a meticulously documented history of professional care. Every detail, from the pristine upholstery to the flawless exterior finish, confirms its status as a premier acquisition for the most discerning automotive enthusiast. This is a rare opportunity to secure a vehicle of unrivaled integrity and performance.",
