    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a bit sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been my pride and joy, always garaged and pampered. You won't find a single scratch or hiccup here. It runs like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to tell you more about it!",
      "price": 46500.0,
